    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dents on the rear quarter panel, and clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat, though all major electronics are functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and aging suspension components. It is a functional car that has been used daily, but it is certainly not a showpiece.",
