    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to the highest possible standards. This specimen exhibits no discernible wear, retaining its original showroom luster both internally and externally. Accompanied by a comprehensive service history and a rigorous multi-point inspection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
